+~+~+~+~+~+~+~+~+~+~[b][u]WELCOME TO THE SWINTELLSOFT DEVELOPMENT[/u][/b]~+~+~+~+~+~
Hello, Im Eric and Ive finally decided to acaully start back up SwintellSoft.After I was gone for so long I continued to sorta code on the server but just a little.The server was originally based off ricscape v3 but i redid alot of things.I have complete website and forums I am however willing sometimes to pay rl cash for things that make the server better.I am a dedicated leader and a somewhat good coder. I need a team of developers to help me create a damb good server from what it once was!
Swintell once had about 50 players online average and 97 recorded max that I know of.
---------------------------------------[b]JOB OFFERS AND APPLICATIONS![/b]----------------------------
First off I need a hoster worse than anything... they will get w/e they want lol as long as they dont abuse their powers as a server hoster!
[b]job 1 server hoster[/b] ---name: ---hotmail: ---internetspeed: ---age: ---will you host 24/7? ---will you archive server when I and the team of coders need to edit? ---are you loyal -------what do you want on the server (items crowns cash unlimited health ect)
[b]job 2 server coder[/b] ---name: ---age: ---experiance coding? ---no need of proof just let you know if you cant code you will be kicked out ---hotmail:?(need hotmail...) -----will you be a loyal member and developer and help me with codes
[b]job 3 client coder[/b] ---name: ---age: ---experiance client coding? ---no need for real proof just know youll be kicked out if you dont know what your doing ----know that all items will be created and made by you and your fellow client coders --- me myself am not a very good client coder --- able to make a good client without glitches?
[b]job 4 webclient maker[/b] ---name: ---age: ---experiance with clients and HTML? --- no proof just know you should know what you doing... --- I have a website specificly for webclient already....just do you best to get it on it ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
All SwintellSoft developers will get a gold crown and owner rights ingame and will recieve forum admin. please do not post flames =) thank you
[b]contact me from my email[/b] yahoo:eric_dybwad (thats my yahoo messenger) email: Eric@swintell.com it is a version of hotmail (just comes through my website)
